item-description:
Make your artwork or photograph look pricey that it deserves. Cellophane bags. HIGH QUALITY 1.6mils ULTRA CLEAR WITH 40MM SELF SEAL STRIP ALONG TOP EDGE.

TO FIT 11x17 PRINTS OR CARDS WITH A BACKING BOARD. Exclusively designed to have stronger seams than those available elsewhere. 

Designed specifically for creators, these bags are perfect for storing and protecting your valuable artwork. Made from high-quality, durable plastic, they're designed to keep your creations safe from moisture, dust, and other potential hazards. 

With their clear design, these bags also allow you to showcase your art and prints without ever having to take them out of the packaging. And thanks to their convenient size, they're ideal for a wide range of different pieces. 

Additionally, these 11x17 clear plastic bags are designed to have just enough wiggle room to accommodate a backing board, making them perfect for matting and framing your art and prints. Whether you're a professional artist, a photographer, or just a hobbyist, these bags offer the protection and versatility you need to keep your creations in pristine condition. 

So go ahead and order yours today - your artwork deserves the best! So if you're looking for a simple, affordable, and effective way to protect your artwork, look no further than these 11x17 clear plastic bags. 

Order yours today and start enjoying the peace of mind that comes with knowing your creations are safe and sound.
